<br>
I think what was implied is soloing in places higher up the ladder than SolA. Almost everyone can solo in SolA, but how many under 55 warriors do you know that can solo PoJ? I did witness at various times a necro, a ranger, a wizzy, and of course a druid all under 55 destroying their mobs in PoJ single handedly (am I missing any other classes that can do it?)<br>
<br>
As far as warriors being useless in groups with knights when they are not MT,  I have to totally disagree. A good warrior will be able to offtank and be a melee type of crowd controller; a good warrior will be able to interrupt casters when needed (seen a whole lot of that in LDoN); a good warrior will be able to step in and save the group from a wipe when needed. Warriors are a great class, cheer up; they just need a little fix here and there.<br>
<br>
/hijack on<br>
